---
By: Shantideva
Source:
  Chapter: 8
  Title: Guide to the Bodhisattva's Way of Life
  Verse: 137
Tags:
  - return
  - compassion
Title: The Bodhisattva Vow
---
I completely dedicate myself to the happiness of others.
From now on, I must hold this clearly and truly,
And not think of anything
Other than benefiting all living beings.
